access_token <- get_spotify_access_token()

# get features, genre and name of artist
top_50songs <- function(uri){
  playlist = get_playlist_tracks(uri,NULL,100,0,NULL,access_token, FALSE) 

  features = get_playlist_audio_features("spotify",uri,access_token)

  id <- list()
  name <- list()
  genre <- list()
  for (i in playlist$track.album.artists){
    id <- append(id,i$id[1])
    name <- append(name, i$name[1])
  }
  for (i in id){
    genre <- append(genre,get_artist(i, access_token)$genres[1])
  }

  playlist$genre <- genre
  playlist$name <- name
  playlist <- merge(playlist,features, by="track.uri",all.x=TRUE)
  playlist <- playlist[-c(2:12,14:18,21:30,32:40,45:47,59:102)]
  return(playlist)
}

reorder_cormat <- function(cormat){
# Use correlation between variables as distance
dd <- as.dist((1-cormat)/2)
hc <- hclust(dd)
cormat <-cormat[hc$order, hc$order]
}
